<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7fb; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #4880FF 100%); padding: 36px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
        .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 14px; margin: 0; }
        .content { padding: 28px 30px; }
        .stat-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .stat-box { flex: 1; background: #f0f9ff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; text-align: center; }
        .stat-box .num { font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; color: #0ea5e9; display: block; }
        .stat-box .lbl { font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }
        .highlight-box { background: #eff6ff; border-left: 4px solid #4880FF; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .highlight-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1e40af; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>👋 We Miss You, <%= seekerName %>!</h1>
                <p>Here's what happened on JobSpark while you were away</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #334155;">Hi <strong><%= seekerName %></strong>,</p>
                <p style="color: #475569;">It's been <strong><%= daysSinceLastVisit %> days</strong> since you last visited JobSpark. A lot has happened — don't miss out!</p>

                <div class="stat-row">
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <span class="num"><%= newJobsCount %>+</span>
                        <span class="lbl">New Jobs Posted</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <span class="num"><%= newCompaniesCount %>+</span>
                        <span class="lbl">Companies Hiring</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-box">
                        <span class="num"><%= hiringCitiesCount %></span>
                        <span class="lbl">Cities Active</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <p>🔥 <strong><%= activeHiringCount %> companies</strong> are actively hiring in <strong><%= topCity %></strong> right now!</p>
                </div>

                <p style="color: #475569;">Your profile is still live and being viewed by recruiters. Log back in to see who's been looking at your profile and apply to the latest opportunities.</p>

                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/jobs" class="btn">See What You Missed →</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>You received this because you haven't visited in a while.<br>
                <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>" style="color: #0ea5e9;">Visit JobSpark</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
